# Videos Folder

Place your video files here. Supported formats: MP4, WebM, MOV

## Recommended Video Specifications:
- Format: MP4 (H.264 codec)
- Resolution: 1920x1080 (Full HD) or higher
- Aspect Ratio: 16:9
- File Size: Optimize for web (consider compression)
- Duration: 10-30 seconds for hero videos (looping)

## Usage:
- Hero video: `/assets/videos/hero-video.mp4`
- Research page videos: `/assets/videos/research-[name].mp4`

## Example files you can add:
- `hero-video.mp4` - Main homepage hero video
- `robotics-video.mp4` - Robotics research page video
- `ai-video.mp4` - AI research page video
- etc.
